OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain soon
OL,6,Fclearing Shetland in the evening.
OL,7,FOtherwise clear spells and scattered
OL,8,Fblustery showers, heavy at times.
OL,9,FStrong southwest winds with coastal
OL,10,Fgales possible later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FBright spells and scattered
OL,13,Fshowers in the morning, showers
OL,14,Fbecoming less frequent in the
OL,15,Fafternoon allowing longer sunny
OL,16,Fspells. Strong southwest winds at
OL,17,Ffirst, veering westerly and easing in
OL,18,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
