OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry with bright spells on Saturday,
OL,7,Fthe odd shower possible. Stronger
OL,8,Fsoutherly winds on Sunday and Monday
OL,9,Fwith variable cloud and occasional
OL,10,Foutbreaks of rain.
